description:
We have a case where a promotion rule appears to have evaluated false when we would have expected it to evaluate true.

*_FYI there will be additional history on the linked ticket_*

Promotion id 2152 on orgid 9000134 is “S13: Complete Your Colorectal Cancer Screening Fitkit_v31”, and member with external id {{oWsJgifLvHErFad2diTarBcKZmk5fYBB+3t:UOWK5jn9}} should have received the benefit  from event id {{c4ee7066-61c0-4f72-8f33-691b7fdcd93c}}

We need some help trying to identify why this rule would have evaluated false.

_it does seem that there could be a tie-in with a previous change that was made as the issue only seems to have happened after that change. See linked tickets for further details of that change_



@Nitish Reddy and @Bhagya Yasam please feel free to update this ticket as needed in case I misstated anything.

