description:
For orgId -4 reon_data_fnb response time is high which is causing to increase in overall response time.
below are finding:

reon_data_fnb( orgId:4 ) is demo organization.



We are getting below request for orgId 4:

requestId: {{4b742944}}-b193-4dbf-9c7e-e86ddaee0b7d (Taking 45MS)

{{2025-02-27T18:55:14.229262906Z stdout F 2025-02-27 12:55:14.228 [pool-17-thread-1371] [getcc_2795092] [d72f3d4c5fbb92ff69df4ea3eeafb4ce] [4b742944}}-b193-4dbf-9c7e-e86ddaee0b7d{{] [4] [c.c.l.i.e.LuciThriftServiceImpl:830] [DEBUG] received call for getCouponConfiguration : GetCouponConfigRequest(requestId:d72f3d4c5fbb92ff69df4ea3eeafb4ce, orgId:4, ownedBy:JOURNEY, ownerId:0, orderBy:LAST_MODIFIED_DATE, sort:DESC, limit:20, uploadInfoRequired:true, includeUnclaimed:true}}

request id: {{b5e9eb91-}}c4a3-4b97-8507-fd67df4abd73(Taking 10s)

{{2025-02-27T18:51:51.802679323Z stdout F 2025-02-27 12:51:51.802 [pool-17-thread-1370] [getcc_2794762] [0dca0855ed5458f496e192eb654d00c2] [b5e9eb91-}}c4a3-4b97-8507-fd67df4abd73{{] [4] [c.c.l.i.e.LuciThriftServiceImpl:830] [DEBUG] received call for getCouponConfiguration : GetCouponConfigRequest(requestId:0dca0855ed5458f496e192eb654d00c2, orgId:4, orderBy:LAST_MODIFIED_DATE, sort:DESC, limit:20, uploadInfoRequired:true}}



Here if we get {{includeUnclaimed:true}} in request then response time is high.

After further debugging both request id’s are using diffrent query to{{CouponSeriesDaoImpl}}. {{findCouponSeriesIdsByFilter}}

requestId: {{4b742944}}-b193-4dbf-9c7e-e86ddaee0b7d (Taking 45MS)

{{SELECT voucher_series.id FROM luci.voucher_series  LEFT OUTER JOIN luci.owner_info ON voucher_series.id = owner_info.coupon_series_id AND voucher_series.org_id = owner_info.org_id WHERE voucher_series.org_id = :voucher_series.org_id  AND (owner_info.owned_by = 'NONE' OR owner_info.owned_by = 'JOURNEY')  AND (owner_info.owner_id = -1 OR owner_info.owner_id = 0)  AND ( IF(voucher_series.valid_till_date IS NOT NULL, voucher_series.valid_till_date, owner_info.expiry_date)  >= '2025-02-28 00:00:00' OR  IF(voucher_series.valid_till_date IS NOT NULL, voucher_series.valid_till_date, owner_info.expiry_date)  IS NULL)  ORDER BY last_used DESC LIMIT 0 ,20}}



request id: {{b5e9eb91-}}c4a3-4b97-8507-fd67df4abd73(Taking 10ms)

{{SELECT voucher_series.id FROM luci.voucher_series  LEFT OUTER JOIN luci.owner_info ON voucher_series.id = owner_info.coupon_series_id AND voucher_series.org_id = owner_info.org_id WHERE voucher_series.org_id = :voucher_series.org_id  AND ( IF(voucher_series.valid_till_date IS NOT NULL, voucher_series.valid_till_date, owner_info.expiry_date)  >= '2025-02-28 00:00:00' OR  IF(voucher_series.valid_till_date IS NOT NULL, voucher_series.valid_till_date, owner_info.expiry_date)  IS NULL)  ORDER BY last_used DESC LIMIT 0 ,20}}



After checking the query we get to know we are not using the correct index for {{`org_id`,`owned_by`,`owner_id`}}.

*Fix for issue:*

Create a new index : {{KEY `orgOwnedByOwnerId` (`org_id`,`owned_by`,`owner_id`),}}

